体的亮度越来越低——这种情况在白炽灯和荧光灯上更明显。所有LED灯也避免不了光衰，不过它的光衰速度是比较慢的，一般用肉眼很难看出变化。但也不排除劣质LED，或劣质光珠板，或由于散热不良等客观因素，导致LED光衰速度变快。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200523/1590201841125175.jpg\" title=\"1590030633629501.jpg\" alt=\"timg.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">二、灯珠坏了</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">LED芯片本身是由一个一个的灯珠组合而成，如果其中一个或一部分不亮了，则势必会使得整个灯具发暗。灯珠一般是先串联再并联，所以某一个灯珠烧毁，就有可能导致一批灯珠都不亮了。烧毁后的灯珠表面有明显的黑点，找到它，用一根电线接在它的背面，将它短路；或者更换一个新灯珠，都可以解决问题。LED偶尔烧毁一个，可能是碰巧了。如果频繁烧毁，则要考虑驱动器问题，驱动器故障的另外一个表现，就是烧毁灯珠。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200523/1590201841232927.jpg\" title=\"1590030646917931.jpg\" alt=\"u=1049625902,3495134387&amp;fm=26&amp;gp=0_副本.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">三、驱动器损坏</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">LED灯珠要求在直流低电压（20V以下）工作，但我们平时的市电是交流高电压（交流220V）。把市电变成灯珠需要的电，就需要一个装置，叫做“LED恒流驱动电源”。理论上来讲，只要驱动器的参数与灯珠板相匹配，就可以持续供电、正常使用。驱动器内部比较复杂，任何一个装置（比如电容、整流器等等）发生故障，都有可能引起输出电压的改变，进而引起灯具发暗。驱动器损坏是LED灯具中最常见的一种故障，通常更换驱动器后，就可以解决。</span></p><p><br/></p>','2020-05-23 02:44:02','2020-05-23 02:44:02',1,5,1),(6,1,4,'太阳能led路灯头需要具备哪些条件','太阳能led路灯头需要具备哪些条件','太阳能led路灯头需要具备哪些条件','太阳能led路灯头需要具备哪些条件','images/158985533327[1].jpg','','澳镭照明-新闻部',32,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">led路灯头作为一款新型的半导体照明设备，光源稳定性、防护等级和便捷性方面都有着更加强大的突出优点，而也正是有着这些强大的优势，所以能获得更多消费者的信赖。那么，led路灯头本身到底具备哪些突出的特点呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200523/1590201963205962.jpg\" title=\"1589855285958279.jpg\" alt=\"微信截图_20200513154940.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">1、价格低廉且维护成本低</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">优质耐用的led路灯头本身具备较强的自洁能力，因其选用特殊的除静电材料制作而成，所以其表面不会粘附过多的灰尘或者水分，而这也能减少用户去定期清洁的成本，另外，与传统的照明设备对比，led路灯头在价格上会更具优势。产品的材料采购及制作成本会远低于传统的灯具，所以能为消费者提供更低廉的产品价格。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">2、节能环保性</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">业内领先的路灯头在节能环保性方面有着更大的优势，因该led灯是采用绿色照明技术，所以在深夜期间会自动降低亮度并缩短照明的时间。其次，led路灯头在红外和紫外性方面的辐射也会大大小于传统的产品，在生产和使用时都不会对外界环境产生任何污染，因此这也是该led路灯头所具备优秀的节能环保特点。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">3、光源稳定性</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">易于使用的路灯头有着较高的光源稳定性，该灯具选用进口光源芯片，其表面则选用了具备防爆、防水性能好的优质钢化玻璃材料，所以能很好的保护灯具并能在长时间的照明使用下也可以保持稳定持久的发光发亮状态，为人们提供亮度更高的光源。</span></p><p><br/></p>','2020-05-23 02:46:04','2020-05-23 02:46:04',1,6,2),(7,1,4,'太阳能路灯用的是什么电池','太阳能路灯用的是什么电池','太阳能路灯用的是什么电池','太阳能路灯用的是什么电池','images/158961143938[2].jpg','','澳镭照明-新闻部',32,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">锂电池体积小，重量轻，便于运输，与同功率太阳能路灯用铅酸胶体电池相比，重量约为三分之一，体积约为三分之一。因此运输更容易，运输成本自然下降。锂电池能量密度高，寿命长。能量密度是指储存在一定空间或质量单位内的能量量。电池的能量密度越大，单位重量或体积所储存的电量就越多。影响锂电池寿命的因素很多，其中能量密度是最重要的内部因素之一。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200523/1590202006164370.jpg\" title=\"1589611259712276.jpg\" alt=\"微信截图_20200516141124.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">太阳能路灯采用锂电池安装方便，传统太阳能路灯安装时需要预留一个电池坑，再将电池放入地下箱内密封。锂太阳能路灯的安装更加方便，锂电池可以直接安装在支架上，使用悬挂式或内置式，同时锂离子太阳能路灯也易于维护。锂离子太阳能路灯在维护过程中只需要将电线杆或电池板上的电池取出即可。与锂电池点焊机生产的锂太阳能路灯相比，传统的太阳能路灯需要挖掘地下电池，进行维护更多的麻烦。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">我相信每个人都熟悉电池，知道它需要储存电能。锂电池组装设备太阳能LED路灯的电池也是如此，它也被用来储存电力和提供照明。其类型一般有铅酸蓄电池、镍镉蓄电池、镍氢蓄电池。然而在路灯照明中，使用的胶体铅酸蓄电池较多。它可以满足夜间照明的前提，储存白天太阳能产生的能量，储存能量以满足连续雨夜照明的照明需求。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200523/1590202006236696.jpg\" title=\"1589611275398005.jpg\" alt=\"微信截图_20200516141219.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">电池的容量如果太小，就不能满足夜间照明的需要。同时电池容量过大，电池就会处于断电状态，影响电池的使用寿命，也会造成一定的浪费，增加不必要的成本。18650锂电池不是一个简单的整体，它需要匹配太阳能光伏电池板和负载功率。这样就可以充分利用其功能，提供电能的存储功能。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">太阳能路灯的一些组成部分，每一个部分都是非常重要的，所以我们必须注意它。对于太阳能路灯的电池来说，它是保证照明的基础，所以必须选择和使用正确的。</span></p><p><br/></p>','2020-05-23 02:47:08','2020-05-23 02:47:08',1,7,3),(8,1,4,'2020深紫外线LED应用市场与品牌策略','2020深紫外线LED应用市场与品牌策略','2020深紫外线LED应用市场与品牌策略','2020深紫外线LED应用市场与品牌策略','images/98077af77b08f0904bf5060ab545aae6.jpg','','澳镭照明-新闻部',32,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">根据Trend Force LED研究(LEDinside)，最新《2020深紫外线LED应用市场与品牌策略》报告指出，展望2020年，相较于过去UV LED厂商依赖价格竞争获取品牌与消费者市场接受度，近来在新型冠状病毒 (COVID-19) 影响之下，品牌与消费者对于杀菌净化的意识大为提升，UV-C LED厂商于农历年后询问度大幅增加，相信UV-C LED也将有机会稳定提升市场产值。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20200523/1590202083964721.png\" title=\"1589530923592717.png\" alt=\"微信截图_20200515160041.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">紫外线汞灯产品优势为光功率高，主要应用在大型空间杀菌与消毒，如学校与医院。然而，UV LED无须预热时间 (Warm-up Time)、不使用汞，所以具有环保、寿命长、节能、热损失较少等优点。除此之外，UV-C LED 仅使用单一波段与光功率仍须提升，照射安全顾虑较小。加上光源小型化的优势，可充分对应到小型空间与表面杀菌的市场需求。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">TrendForce研究经理吴盈洁表示，UV-C LED厂商耕耘家电品牌领域多年，随着UV-C LED 技术稳定与品牌接受度提升，2020年终于可迎来成长爆发点。相较于家电品牌市场，商业应用领域对于UV-C LED产品价格接受度较高。接下来UV-C LED则可望进入商业空调、表面杀菌与净水领域。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">此外，由于车内空气较为封闭，若未与外面空气对流，食物香烟的味道、香水的气味，甚至是乘客带来的细菌与病毒，很容易一直存留车内，造成异味且容易传染生病。2020年乘用车市场计划导入UV-C LED外置杀菌产品与内置空调杀菌模块，提升空气洁净能力。深紫外线 LED 包含UV-B LED与UV-C LED，2020年众多应用随之发展，然而优劣产品质量共存市场导致市场秩序略为混乱。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">TrendForce 2020 深紫外线 LED 应用市场与品牌策略报告交叉分析UV-C LED应用与销售渠道，其营销渠道包含家电市场、商业空间、车用领域、净水潜在市场等，并探讨各渠道品牌的计划与动向。并专章讨论特殊照明市场趋势，涵盖杀菌照明、食品业应用、渔业应用、植物照明、光疗与固化设备市场趋势与实际案例分析。相信能为读者在DUV LED应用发展与销售提供全面布局！</span></p><p><br/></p>','2020-05-23 02:48:06','2020-05-23 02:48:06',1,8,4),(9,1,3,'疫情对各行各业影响重大，led照明行业也不例外！','疫情对各行各业影响重大，led照明行业也不例外！','疫情对各行各业影响重大，led照明行业也不例外！','疫情对各行各业影响重大，led照明行业也不例外！','images/158685592859[1].jpg','','澳镭照明-新闻部',32,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino San