-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">2020年，照明行业迎来了一个艰难的开局。</span></p><p><br/></p>','2020-05-23 02:49:14','2020-05-23 02:49:14',1,9,1),(10,1,3,'LED灯、荧光灯、卤素灯、白炽灯，哪种光源对眼睛伤害最小？','LED灯、荧光灯、卤素灯、白炽灯，哪种光源对眼睛伤害最小？','LED灯、荧光灯、卤素灯、白炽灯，哪种光源对眼睛伤害最小？','LED灯、荧光灯、卤素灯、白炽灯，哪种光源对眼睛伤害最小？','images/156566835034[2].png','','澳镭照明-新闻部',32,'<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">暑假结束后马上就是开学季，一盏好的台灯对学生党来说自然必不可少。而对家长来说，为孩子选购一盏好台灯，重要性绝不低于人手一本的学习利器——《5年X考 3年模拟》！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;当然，有些心很大的父母，没把台灯当一回事，觉得用房间里的吸顶灯也可以，这个做法是万万不可的，绝对会影响到孩子的视力！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">那么，对于学习台灯来说，LED灯、荧光灯、卤素灯、白炽灯，哪种光源对眼睛伤害最小呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565664964265252.png\" title=\"1565664964265252.png\" alt=\"台灯伤害眼睛的情况有哪些.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;主要影响因素：一、不够亮 ; 二、刺眼 ; 三、闪烁。这三个因素，会直接伤害到你眼睛，造成你眼睛疲劳、近视。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;间接影响因素：一、显色性很差 ; 二、光色用错。这两个因素，可能不会直接伤害你的眼睛，但会让你的眼睛觉得不舒服，当然，还有坐姿不当等其它影响因素。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667594926187.png\" title=\"1565667594926187.png\" alt=\"真的有护眼灯吗.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;市面上，不少卖台灯的商家，在推广台灯时，会标上“护眼灯”的字眼。其实，在真正的定义里，并没有一个叫护眼灯的东西，一般市面上所说的护眼灯，大多指的都是以前的荧光灯管（我们暂且把这个“护眼灯”纳入荧光灯，方便我们下面作对比）。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在2018年新修订的《读写作业台灯性能要求》内，也没有标注任何与&quot;护眼&quot;相关的功能性字眼，换句话说，“护眼灯”只是一种概念产品。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667611285170.png\" title=\"1565667611285170.png\" alt=\"台灯选购指标你知多少.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;对于学习台灯来说，有什么参数可以去衡量“护不护眼”？按照在2018年新修订的《读写作业台灯性能要求》标准，台灯必须在照度、照度均匀度、色温、频闪等方面符合相关指标。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;因此，如果你想选好一盏好台灯，必须提前做好功课，了解一下频闪、照度、色温等专业名词的含义，做到选购心里有数！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667627585362.png\" title=\"1565667627585362.png\" alt=\"1频闪.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;很多台灯的一大卖点就是无频闪，既然提到无频闪，你要先弄懂什么是频闪。大多数LED灯都存在频闪现象，因为日常用电是220V 50Hz的交流电，而LED灯本身对电流的反应很明显，电流越大，光越亮，电流越小，光越不亮，这样就造成了频闪。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;上面提到的50Hz交流电，指一秒电流完成50次正弦波形转换，普通台灯多数使用50Hz的交流电进行工作，这时每秒钟会产生100次的明暗相间的闪烁现像，由明变暗，再由暗变明（人眼能感知的变化在30Hz以内，每秒100次的灯光变化)。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565668179561644.gif\" title=\"1565668179561644.gif\" alt=\"640.gif\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;对于这些变化，大脑其实也分辨不出来，但控制瞳孔收缩等眼部肌肉，却可以察觉到这些变化，如果频闪过大，肌肉会长时间处于紧张工作状态，造成视觉疲劳，损伤视力。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;因此，很多市面上的护眼灯，其实是通过增加电容、改善电器电路等方法，来调节工作电流，从而降低或消除频闪。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667639509820.png\" title=\"1565667639509820.png\" alt=\"2眩光.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;眩光（Dazzle）是指视野中由于不适宜亮度分布，或在空间或时间上存在极端的亮度对比，以致引起视觉不舒适和降低物体可见度的视觉条件。眩光是引起视觉疲劳的重要原因之一 。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;眩光可分为直接眩光，反射眩光及对比眩光。一般而言，刺眼眩光在30秒至60秒内，即会对眼睛视力的健康产生明显危害。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;而反射眩光即一般俗称的反光，会使影像模糊化，容易造成眼睛疲劳，阅读吃力，甚至进一步造成眼睛酸痛及头痛的问题。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565668167568182.png\" title=\"1565668167568182.png\" alt=\"防眩光效果不佳.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565668160639435.png\" title=\"1565668160639435.png\" alt=\"防眩光效果较佳.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;据统计，在学习压力大的童鞋中，有55.9%的受访者在使用台灯时，经常有眼睛酸痛，揉眼睛等困扰。童鞋在阅读时感到的不适感，很多都是眩光问题造成的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667648619402.png\" title=\"1565667648619402.png\" alt=\"3显色指数.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;显色指数是表示色彩真实性的指标，一般显色指数越高，表示在这类灯光下的物体颜色越接近真实颜色。国家标准GB/T 9473-2017《读写作业台灯性能要求》对读写台灯的一般显色指数规定不低于80。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565668137286480.png\" title=\"1565668137286480.png\" alt=\"左边显色差，右边显色好.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;同样，在《中小学学校教室采光和照明卫生标准》中指出，教室照明光源的显色指数也不宜小于80。过低的教室照明显色指数影响学生眼晴对物体色彩的识别，使物体不能呈现出其真正的颜色，这种情况如果持续下去，会导致辨色能力的下降和衰退，造成学生的色盲色弱等严重的视力问题和眼部疾病。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 13