; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;因此孩子用的台灯，显指（Ra）至少要高于80。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667660420533.png\" title=\"1565667660420533.png\" alt=\"4照度.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0