style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565668111475793.png\" title=\"1565668111475793.png\" alt=\"建筑照明设计标准.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;照度可以简单理解为灯够不够亮，数值越大越好。而照度均匀度就是光照得够不够均匀，数值越小越均匀。桌面照度在700-1000（lx）为佳。照射范围要有一定的高度，灯光照射面要较大，较均匀。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565668027569364.png\" title=\"1565668027569364.png\" alt=\"灯光满铺整个工作台面，且达到AA级国家读写照度.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;此外，国标对台灯的照度及均匀度做出了要求，分为A和AA两个照度等级。AA等级要比A等级的台灯要好。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565668004758576.png\" title=\"1565668004758576.png\" alt=\"台灯照度及照度.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667670156514.png\" title=\"1565667670156514.png\" alt=\"5色温.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;色温是表示光源光色的尺度，单位为K(开尔文)。通常人眼所见到的光线，是由7种色光的光谱所组成。但其中有些光线偏蓝，有些则偏红，色温就是专门用来量度和计算光线的颜色成分的方法。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;通俗的讲就是色温数值越小，越偏向黄色暖光，数值越大，越偏向冷光。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667983253099.png\" title=\"1565667983253099.png\" alt=\"色温表.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;根据国家规定，色温可调节的LED灯具，如色温超过4000K，应有下述内容的警示语：建议夜间色温调至4000K以下。色温不可调节的台灯，如果色温标称高于4000K的LED灯具，应包括下述内容警示语：其不适合夜晚使用。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;因此，太暖的光，孩子一会儿就疲劳，太白的光，也就是色温太高，会让孩子过于兴奋，做完作业睡不着觉。4000K左右的色温让人在清醒中又有着温暖的感觉，这种色温下读书学习心境平和效率高。因此，色温3000K~4000K的暖白光比较符合学龄儿童的视觉需求。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667685389303.png\" title=\"1565667685389303.png\" alt=\"63c.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3C认证的全称为“中国强制性产品认证”，英文名称 China Compulsory Certification，英文缩写CCC。它是中国政府为保护消费者人身安全和国家安全、加强产品质量管理、依照法律法规实施的一种产品合格评定制度。需要注意的是，3C标志并不是质量标志，它是一种最基础的安全认证。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667969458265.png\" title=\"1565667969458265.png\" alt=\"3c.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;作为一个学习台灯，我们要求至少要过3C的安全认证。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667715852395.png\" title=\"1565667715852395.png\" alt=\"什么才是合适的台灯光源.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;前面讲了这么多干货，现在我们用照度、眩光、频闪、显色、色温这几个指标，总结对比一下什么光源才算是合适的台灯光源呢？</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我们通过一张表格来对比一下。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://m.aooled.com/Upload/ueditor/image/20190813/1565667956642890.png\" title=\"1565667956642890.png\" alt=\"台灯光源对比.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;①LED灯是个变形金刚，频闪可能是很多劣质的LED灯中容易出现的问题，所以挑选的时候要注意频闪的因素。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;②所谓的护眼灯，也就是我们说的荧光灯，在眩光方面会比较差，因为那个节能灯管特别粗，很难控好光，一般都会有眩光，在显色性方面，荧光灯也一般比较差。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;③作为传统光源的白炽灯，一般不够亮 ; 眩光方面，白炽灯由于它灯泡比较大，因此一般也会比较刺眼 ; 色温方面，白炽灯就渣了，因为它只有2700K，甚至2500K，色温太低了，容易造成眼睛疲劳。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;④另一个传统光源卤素灯，有的还是够亮的，色温方面一般可以做到3000K或3300K以上。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border-width: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(133, 133, 133); font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); -webkit-appearance: none; list-style-type: none; border